| Step                            | If fails           | Root Cause            |
| ------------------------------- | ------------------ | --------------------- |
| Source RUNNING but no Kafka msg | MQ channel / queue | MQ side issue         |
| Kafka msg OK but sink fails     | MQ OUT queue       | Channel / permissions |
| Connect fails auth              | SCRAM mismatch     | KafkaUser config      |
| No plugins                      | Image issue        | Wrong base image      |

